{"pin":"BH00718","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00718","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-'Ali","first_line":"O Ali! From the day when that promised Tablet - which hath been designated as the Cry, the Hour and the Trumpet - was dispatched, the ungodly [3.5s]... ...The voice of the Divine Herald, proceeding out of the throne of God, declareth: O ye My loved ones! Suffer not the hem of My sacred vesture","first_line_orig":"یا علی از یومی که لوح معهود که به صیحه و ساعه و صور نامیده شده ارسال گشت مشرکین  ","language":"5","word_count":"1090","subjects":"@defending the Faith; protecting the Cause; apologetics, @status of material wealth; wealth and poverty, @rejection, opposition and persecution, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @work as worship, @fairmindedness; personal justice [insaf], @honesty; truthfulness; trustworthiness","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#45\"\u003eLL#045\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"